#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:71
msgid "Tweaks"
msgstr "Axustes"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:73
msgid ""
"Tweaks are small changes that you can specify to control various aspects of "
"calibre's behavior. You can change them by going to "
"Preferences->Advanced->Tweaks. The default values for the tweaks are "
"reproduced below"
msgstr "Os axustes son pequenas modificacións que podes especificar para controlar varios aspectos do comportamento de Calibre. Podes cambialas indo a Preferencias->Avanzado->Axustes. Os valores predeterminados para os axustes reprodúcense a continuación."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:80
msgid "Overriding icons, templates, et cetera"
msgstr "Anulación de iconas, modelos, etc."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:83
msgid ""
"calibre has direct support for icon themes, there are several icon themes "
"available for calibre, that you can use by going to "
":guilabel:`Preferences->Interface->Look & Feel->Change icon theme`. It is "
"preferable to use icon themes over overriding individual icons."
msgstr "Calibre ten soporte directo para temas de iconas; hai varios temas de iconas dispoñibles para Calibre que podes usar indo a :guilabel:`Preferencias->Interface->Aspecto->Cambiar tema de iconas`. É preferible usar temas de iconas en lugar de sobrescribir iconas individuais."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:88
msgid ""
"calibre allows you to override the static resources, like icons, JavaScript "
"and templates for the metadata jacket, catalogs, etc. with customized "
"versions that you like.  All static resources are stored in the resources "
"sub-folder of the calibre install location. On Windows, this is usually "
":file:`C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Calibre2\\\\app\\\\resources`. On macOS, "
":file:`/Applications/calibre.app/Contents/Resources/resources/`. On Linux, "
"if you are using the binary installer from the calibre website it will be "
":file:`/opt/calibre/resources`. These paths can change depending on where "
"you choose to install calibre."
msgstr "Calibre permíteche anular os recursos estáticos, como iconas, JavaScript e modelos para a funda de metadatos, catálogos, etc., con versións personalizadas que che gusten. Todos os recursos estáticos almacénanse na subcartafol de recursos da localización de instalación de Calibre. En Windows, isto adoita ser :file:`C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Calibre2\\\\app\\\\resources`. En macOS, :file:`/Applications/calibre.app/Contents/Resources/resources/`. En Linux, se estás a usar o instalador binario do sitio web de Calibre, será :file:`/opt/calibre/resources`. Estas rutas poden cambiar dependendo de onde escollas instalar Calibre."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:97
msgid ""
"You should not change the files in this resources folder, as your changes "
"will get overwritten the next time you update calibre. Instead, go to "
":guilabel:`Preferences->Advanced->Miscellaneous` and click :guilabel:`Open "
"calibre configuration folder`. In this configuration folder, create a sub-"
"folder called resources and place the files you want to override in it. "
"Place the files in the appropriate sub folders, for example place images in "
":file:`resources/images`, etc. calibre will automatically use your custom "
"file in preference to the built-in one the next time it is started."
msgstr "Non deberías modificar os ficheiros desta carpeta de recursos, xa que os cambios sobrescribiranse a próxima vez que actualices Calibre. No seu lugar, vai a :guilabel:`Preferencias->Avanzado->Varios` e fai clic en :guilabel:`Abrir carpeta de configuración de Calibre`. Nesta carpeta de configuración, crea unha subcarpeta chamada recursos e coloca nela os ficheiros que queres sobrescribir. Coloca os ficheiros nas subcarpetas axeitadas, por exemplo, coloca imaxes en :file:`recursos/imaxes`, etc. Calibre usará automaticamente o teu ficheiro personalizado con preferencia ao integrado a próxima vez que se inicie."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:106
msgid ""
"For example, if you wanted to change the icon for the :guilabel:`Remove "
"books` action, you would first look in the built-in resources folder and see"
" that the relevant file is :file:`resources/images/remove_books.png`. "
"Assuming you have an alternate icon in PNG format called "
":file:`my_remove_books.png` you would save it in the configuration folder as"
" :file:`resources/images/remove_books.png`. All the icons used by the "
"calibre user interface are in :file:`resources/images` and its sub-folders. "
"Placing an override file here will have even higher priority than a custom "
"icon theme."
msgstr "Por exemplo, se quixeses cambiar a icona para a acción :guilabel:`Eliminar libros`, primeiro terías que buscar no cartafol de recursos integrado e verías que o ficheiro relevante é :file:`resources/images/remove_books.png`. Supoñendo que tes unha icona alternativa en formato PNG chamada :file:`my_remove_books.png`, gardaríase no cartafol de configuración como :file:`resources/images/remove_books.png`. Todas as iconas usadas pola interface de usuario de Calibre están en :file:`resources/images` e os seus subcartafoles. Colocar un ficheiro de substitución aquí terá unha prioridade aínda maior que un tema de iconas personalizado."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:116
msgid "Creating your own icon theme for calibre"
msgstr "Creando o teu propio tema de iconas para Calibre"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:118
msgid ""
"If you have created a beautiful set of icons and wish to share them with "
"other calibre users via calibre's builtin icon theme support, you can easily"
" package up your icons into a theme. To do so, go to "
":guilabel:`Preferences->Miscellaneous->Create icon theme`, select the folder"
" where you have put your icons. Then fill up the theme metadata and click "
"OK. This will result in a ZIP file containing the theme icons. You can "
"upload that to the calibre forum at `Mobileread "
"<https://www.mobileread.com/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=166>`__ and then I "
"will make your theme available via calibre's builtin icon theme system. By "
"default, the icon theme you just created will also be installed as the "
"current theme in calibre. If you are testing your theme, remember to remove "
"the images from the :file:`resources/images` folder so that the icons from "
"the theme are used."
msgstr "Se creaches un fermoso conxunto de iconas e queres compartilas con outros usuarios de Calibre a través da compatibilidade con temas de iconas integrados en Calibre, podes empaquetar facilmente as túas iconas nun tema. Para facelo, vai a :guilabel:`Preferencias->Varios->Crear tema de iconas`, selecciona o cartafol onde colocaches as túas iconas. Despois, completa os metadatos do tema e fai clic en Aceptar. Isto dará como resultado un ficheiro ZIP que contén as iconas do tema. Podes subilo ao foro de Calibre en `Mobileread <https://www.mobileread.com/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=166>`__ e despois farei que o teu tema estea dispoñible a través do sistema de temas de iconas integrado de Calibre. Por defecto, o tema de iconas que acabas de crear tamén se instalará como tema actual en Calibre. Se estás a probar o teu tema, lembra eliminar as imaxes do cartafol :file:`resources/images` para que se usen as iconas do tema."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:132
msgid ""
"As of calibre 6, you can have custom icons for light and dark mode. Simply "
"create two versions of the icon and name the files with the suffix ``-for-"
"dark-theme`` and ``-for-light-theme``. For example, ``modified-for-dark-"
"theme.png`` and ``modified-for-light-theme.png``. Then calibre will "
"automatically use the appropriate icon based on the current theme."
msgstr "A partir de Calibre 6, podes ter iconas personalizadas para o modo claro e escuro. Simplemente crea dúas versións da icona e nomea os ficheiros co sufixo ``-for-dark-theme`` e ``-for-light-theme``. Por exemplo, ``modified-for-dark-theme.png`` e ``modified-for-light-theme.png``. Entón, Calibre usará automaticamente a icona axeitada segundo o tema actual."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:139
msgid "Customizing calibre with plugins"
msgstr "Personalizar Calibre con complementos"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:141
msgid ""
"calibre has a very modular design. Almost all functionality in calibre comes"
" in the form of plugins. Plugins are used for conversion, for downloading "
"news (though these are called recipes), for various components of the user "
"interface, to connect to different devices, to process files when adding "
"them to calibre and so on. You can get a complete list of all the built-in "
"plugins in calibre by going to :guilabel:`Preferences->Advanced->Plugins`."
msgstr "Calibre ten un deseño moi modular. Case toda a funcionalidade de Calibre vén en forma de complementos. Os complementos úsanse para a conversión, para descargar noticias (aínda que se chaman receitas), para varios compoñentes da interface de usuario, para conectarse a diferentes dispositivos, para procesar ficheiros ao engadilos a Calibre e así sucesivamente. Podes obter unha lista completa de todos os complementos integrados en Calibre indo a :guilabel:`Preferencias->Avanzado->Complementos`."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:148
msgid ""
"You can write your own plugins to customize and extend the behavior of "
"calibre. The plugin architecture in calibre is very simple, see the tutorial"
" :ref:`pluginstutorial`."
msgstr "Podes escribir os teus propios complementos para personalizar e ampliar o comportamento de Calibre. A arquitectura dos complementos en Calibre é moi sinxela; consulta o tutorial :ref:`plugintutorial`."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/customize.rst:152
msgid ""
"Once you have written a plugin, you can upload that to the calibre plugins "
"forum at `Mobileread "
"<https://www.mobileread.com/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=237>`__ and it will be"
" made available via calibre's builtin plugin updater."
msgstr "Unha vez que teñas escrito un complemento, podes subilo ao foro de complementos de Calibre en `Mobileread <https://www.mobileread.com/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=237>`__ e estará dispoñible a través do actualizador de complementos integrado de Calibre."
